sentences: Proposal by Croatia on LULUCF and special circumstances of Croatia under UNFCCC Article 4.6: These issues were presented to the SBI on Tuesday, 2 December.
After informal consultations undertaken by Jim Penman (UK), SBI adopted conclusions and agreed to forward to the COP a draft decision, which was adopted on Friday, 12 December.
enb_long_title: Ninth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
